text: Tulluuwwan isaan tokko kan kaaba Mekkaa gubbaa boqochuun, holqichi addunyaa irraa guutummaatti kan addaan bahee dha.

West Central Oromo: Tulluuwwan isaan tokko kan kaaba Mekkaa gubbaa boqochuun, holqichi addunyaa irraa guutummaatti kan addaan bahee dha. 
English: The Central Oromo: A small, but well-documented, group of people, mostly from the Central Oromo region, are mostly Muslims, and are mostly in the same language as the rest of the population.
